race.comment: ASTON HONCHO (1) turned in a plain effort last time when seventh at this track over 350m behind Gumtree Hill (19.94) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. Has claims if he runs up to expectations. WHITE SHIRAZ (5) is going well, finishing in the placings twice in a row. Not beaten far last time when a one length third (19.60) in a Grade 5 at this track. Can improve sharply here. STILSON (8) produced a modest effort most recently when seventh at Geelong over 460m behind Princess Lass (26.87) in a Grade 5. Key player if finds best. BRAEMAR MOLLY (3) can run a bold race on best form.
